# Issue Tracker — Detailed Conversation Log
**Date:** March 2, 2026 | **Duration:** ~2.5 hours  
**Project:** Unico Connect Issue Tracker (Spring Boot + React)

---

## Phase 1: Backend Startup (08:30 – 09:00)

### Step 1.1 — Explored the project structure
- Found the backend at `c:\Users\Varun Kalyadapu\OneDrive\Desktop\Unicon-Test\issue-tracker-backend`
- Spring Boot 3.2.3, Java 17, PostgreSQL, Lombok, WebSockets
- Read `pom.xml`, `application.properties`, all model/service/controller/config files

### Step 1.2 — First startup attempt failed
```
> mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run
'C:\Program' is not recognized as an internal or external command...
```
**Root cause:** `JAVA_HOME` is `C:\Program Files\Common Files\Oracle\Java\javapath` — the space in "Program Files" breaks unquoted path references in `mvnw.cmd`.

### Step 1.3 — Fixed mvnw.cmd
Modified line 18 to properly quote all variables:
```diff
- %JAVACMD% -cp %WRAPPER_JAR% org.apache.maven.wrapper.MavenWrapperMain %*
+ "%JAVACMD%" "-Dmaven.multiModuleProjectDirectory=%MAVEN_PROJECTBASEDIR%" -cp "%WRAPPER_JAR%" org.apache.maven.wrapper.MavenWrapperMain %*
```

### Step 1.4 — Port 8080 conflict
Backend couldn't start — port 8080 already in use by another Java process. Killed the old process with `Stop-Process`.

### Step 1.5 — Backend started successfully
Used direct PowerShell Java invocation:
```powershell
& "java" "-Dmaven.multiModuleProjectDirectory=$basedir" -cp "$basedir\.mvn\wrapper\maven-wrapper.jar" org.apache.maven.wrapper.MavenWrapperMain spring-boot:run
```
**Result:** `Started IssueTrackerApplication in 14.508 seconds` on port 8080.

