## Phase 7: Swagger API Documentation (15:30 – 15:48)

### Added springdoc-openapi to pom.xml
```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springdoc</groupId>
    <artifactId>springdoc-openapi-starter-webmvc-ui</artifactId>
    <version>2.3.0</version>
</dependency>
```

### Created OpenApiConfig.java
- Title: "Issue Tracker API"
- Description: "REST API for the Unico Connect Issue Tracker"
- Version: "1.0.0"
- Server: `http://localhost:8080`

### Annotated IssueController.java
- `@Tag(name = "Issues", description = "CRUD operations for managing issues")`
- `@Operation` on all 6 endpoints with summaries and descriptions
- `@ApiResponse` for 200, 201, 204, 404, 422 codes
- `@Parameter` on filter parameters (project, priority, status, assignee, search)

### Annotated CommentController.java
- `@Tag(name = "Comments", description = "Manage comments on issues")`
- `@Operation` on GET and POST
- `@ApiResponse` for 200, 201, 404, 422

### Compilation error encountered
```
CommentController.java:[34,48] cannot find symbol: method getComments(java.lang.Long)
```
**Fix:** Changed `getComments(issueId)` to `getCommentsByIssueId(issueId)` to match the service method name.

### Backend restarted successfully
- Swagger UI: ✅ `http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui/index.html` returns 200
- OpenAPI JSON: ✅ `http://localhost:8080/v3/api-docs` returns all 5 paths

